WEBVTT

00:01:29.479 --> 00:01:31.838
And all of these things
have worked in the past.

00:01:31.862 --> 00:01:34.476
But like I said,
this time it was different.

00:01:35.664 --> 00:01:39.038
Michael Brown's death and the subsequent
treatment of the community

00:01:39.062 --> 00:01:42.799
led to a string of protests in and around
Ferguson and St. Louis.

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:47.325
When I got out to those protests
about the fourth or fifth day,

00:01:47.349 --> 00:01:48.752
it was not out of courage;

00:01:49.367 --> 00:01:50.679
it was out of guilt.

00:01:51.495 --> 00:01:52.768
See, I'm black.

00:01:53.223 --> 00:01:54.968
I don't know if y'all noticed that.

00:01:54.992 --> 00:01:56.017
(Laughter)

00:01:56.041 --> 00:02:01.518
But I couldn't sit in St. Louis,
minutes away from Ferguson,